---
const appName = 'AutoStock';
const appNameKr = '오토스톡';
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div>
      <span class="beta-pill">
        <span class="beta-pill-dot">β</span>
        BETA · 비공개 테스트 진행 중
      </span>
      <h1>
        잠든 사이에도,<br/>
        <em>내 전략대로</em> 매매.
      </h1>
      <p class="lede">
        가격 조건을 한 번만 정해두면 24시간 시장을 감시해
        자동으로 매수·매도를 실행합니다. {appNameKr}는 출시 전 베타로,
        QR 한 번이면 바로 체험할 수 있어요.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#install" class="btn btn-primary">
          지금 베타 체험하기
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M3 7h8m0 0L7 3m4 4l-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-secondary">기능 더보기</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <span class="hero-meta-item">
          <span class="pulse-dot"></span>
          실시간 서버 감지 가동 중
        </span>
        <span class="hero-meta-item">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M7 1l1.8 3.6L13 5.3l-3 2.9L10.6 13 7 11l-3.6 2 .6-4.8L1 5.3l4.2-.7L7 1z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          미국 주식 (NAS · NYS)
        </span>
        <span class="hero-meta-item">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="5.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M7 4v3l2 1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          24시간 자동 매매
        </span>
        <span class="hero-meta-item">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><rect x="1.5" y="3" width="11" height="8" rx="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M1.5 6h11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/></svg>
          한국투자증권 계좌 필요
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
      <div class="phone-stage" style="position: relative; width: 360px; height: 580px;">
        <div class="float" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 30px;">
          <div style="width: 315px; height: 681px; border-radius: 48px; background: #0b0f1a; padding: 8px; box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(11,15,26,0.18), 0 0 0 1px rgba(11,15,26,0.10), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.04); position: relative;">
            <div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; border-radius: 42px; overflow: hidden; background: #f2f2f7; position: relative;">
              <img src="/assets/screen-realtime.png" alt="실시간 매매" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;" />
              <div style="position: absolute; top: 11px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 110px; height: 32px; border-radius: 20px; background: #000;"></div>
              <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 120px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ticker-card" style="top: 60px; left: -40px; animation: float 7s ease-in-out infinite;">
          <div class="ticker-sym" style="background: #2563eb;">NV</div>
          <div class="ticker-meta">
            <span class="ticker-name">NVDA · 매수 체결</span>
            <span class="ticker-sub">1주 @ $225.99</span>
          </div>
          <span class="ticker-pct up">-2.0%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ticker-card" style="bottom: 80px; right: -50px; animation: float 9s ease-in-out infinite reverse;">
          <div class="ticker-sym" style="background: #0b0f1a;">TS</div>
          <div class="ticker-meta">
            <span class="ticker-name">TSM · 매도 성공</span>
            <span class="ticker-sub">+2.01% 수익</span>
          </div>
          <span class="ticker-pct up">↑</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
